Consider letting Lux cast her W while moving. 

If you cast Prismatic Barrier while trying to get away from a melee champion that's attacking you, it will often times just let him get an extra auto off. Which puts you in a dissatisfying position - Do you keep running hoping that he doesn't kill you before you get to safety or do you try to use your defensive skill hoping that he doesn't get in the auto which might negate your W and do more damage than if you kept running...

It's a major quality of life improvement.

